# BACK-END EXAMINATION

Project Overview
The goal of this project is to develop a backend API that enables users to retrieve information about islands. The project consists of three phases, each with specific requirements and objectives.

## Phase 1: Design Database Diagram & Phase 2: Implement Retrieve Island List API

    Location: ./src
    Setup:
        python -m venv venv
        venv/scripts/activate
        pip install -r requirements
        py manage.py runserver

## Phase 3: Count the number of islands

    Location: ./phase3.py
    Setup:
        py phase3.py

## Phase 4: Build a Dockerfile to make a Docker image for this project

    src: BACK-END EXAMINATION
    Location: ./Dockerfile
    Setup:
        docker build -t island .
        docker run -d -p 8000:8000 island
